  "title": "Engineering Technician (Joining bonus of $5000)",
  "description": "<p>Engineering Technician<br />Location: Changi<br />Joining Bonus: Up to <strong>$5,000</strong></p><h3><strong>Job Highlights</strong></h3><ul><li>Permanent shift (Morning / Afternoon / Night)</li><li>6-day work week</li><li>Up to <strong>$5,000 joining bonus</strong> (terms apply)</li></ul><h3><strong>Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li>Perform preventive and corrective maintenance on equipment, machinery, and systems.</li><li>Support daily operational activities including handling, inspection, and monitoring of assets or materials.</li><li>Prepare, update, and submit maintenance and operational documentation.</li><li>Liaise with internal departments to resolve technical or operational issues.</li><li>Troubleshoot technical faults and support continuous improvement initiatives.</li><li>Ensure compliance with safety procedures, work instructions, and operational requirements.</li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li>Minimum <strong>Nitec</strong> in relevant fields OR at least <strong>2</strong> <strong>years of relevant work experience</strong>.</li><li>Supervisory or team-leading skills.</li><li>Able to multitask and communicate effectively with airlines and third parties.</li><li>Able to work <strong>permanent shift</strong> and <strong>6 days per week</strong>.</li><li>Able to lift heavy objects.</li></ul><h3><strong>How to Apply</strong></h3><p>Apply Now or a quicker response.<br />We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p><strong>K. Keshika Samantha (R26159509)</strong><br /><strong>Just Recruit Singapore Pte Ltd (EA12C6295)</strong></p>",
